{"word":"G3817 - παίω - paíō - pah'-yo - Smite","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παίω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">paíō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pah'-yo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Smite</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>NA / Not Available</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வெட்டு, அடி, கொட்டு"},{"paragraph":"smite, strike"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>A primary verb; to <i>hit</i> (as if by a single blow and less violently than <a href=\"#/G5180 - τύπτω - týptō - toop'-to/5180\">G5180</a>); specifically to <i>sting</i> (as a scorpion): - smite, strike.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}